title.narrative: The Ultimate Virtuous Cycle of Girls' Education

description.narrative: The vision for this project is to unleash the ultimate virtuous cycle of girls’ education. A critical mass of marginalised girls (the cohort supported under the previous Girls Education Challenge project) will be enabled to transition to, progress through and succeed at secondary school; and create a bridge for them to transition from school to a secure and fulfilling livelihood. From this position as GEC ‘graduates’, they will lead initiatives to support girls’ education within their communities, and join forces with district and national authorities to drive change at a wider scale, resetting the context for future generations of girls.
